---
title: Conversational Customer Support Platfom | NHANCE NOW
"description": "Make it easy for your customers to get response, receive service and access information, 24/7, through realtime personalized conversations."
---
extends layouts/_layout
block content
  .solution.support
    .intro
      .container.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration="1s")
        strong Support
        h2 On demand & conversational
        p Give customers control to resolve queries on their own and get trained with knowledgebases and various DIY channels
    .container.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
      .intro__text
        p A modern customer wants control on how and when to resolve their issues, take training or simply learn about new features and functionalities. 
          strong Nhance now 
          | helps you deliver these through a variety of support channels which are self managing. It transfers control of the support services directly to customers and lets them control the frequency, pace and channel of choice.
    .solution__features
      .container
        h2 Features
        .row.features-scroller__row
          .col-md-6.col-lg-5.offset-lg-1.col-12.order-md-first.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img
              img(src="img/solution/support/support__img-1.jpg", alt="")
          .col-md-6.col-lg-5.col-12.order-first.wow.fadeInRight(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .features-scroller__text
              h3 Do it yourself (DIY)
              p The future of product and services training is “doing it ourselves”. Provide rich media files, on-demand videos, digital documents, tips and tricks to assist customers gain knowledge about your products and services without any external aid.
              p Eliminate the need of human resources for assisting customers and enable anytime, anywhere learning.
        .row.features-scroller__row
          .col-md-6.col-lg-4.offset-lg-2.col-12.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .features-scroller__text
              h3 Help center
              p Modern day customers are impatient. They need resolutions to their queries instantly. Provide instant help via troubleshooting videos, FAQs, remote video support to provide instant gratification to your customers.
              p The self-service section can help reduce the load on your back-office teams by as much as 30%. It can also reduce field visit of technicians and support agents by as much as 70%.
          .col-md-6.col-lg-6.col-12.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img.features-scroller__img--support
              img(src="img/solution/support/support__img-2.jpg", alt="")
        .row.features-scroller__row.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
          .col-md-6.col-lg-5.offset-lg-1.col-12.order-md-first
            .features-scroller__img
              img(src="img/solution/support/support__img-3.jpg", alt="")
          .col-md-6.col-lg-4.col-12.order-first.wow.fadeInRight(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .features-scroller__text
              h3 Live chat
              p Live chat is the best communication platform to offer a real-time support and response to your customers. It has higher satisfaction rates than email and phone.With instant connect to live chat agents and 24/7 availability it is the most non-intrusive channel for customers support enjoying wide popularity.
              p Live chat not only helps your customers start a conversation with you anytime, it also helps youto build long-term relationships with your existing customers.
        